File foo.scala:

```scala
object Foo {
  object X { def unapply(x : Int)(y : Option[Int] = None) = None }
  42 match { case _ X _ => () }
}
```

Trying to compile this with

```scala
scalac foo.scala
```

causes the compiler to crash with an assertion error:

